            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/982443430/photo/mango-juice-or-aam-panna-or-panha-in-a-transparent-glass-with-whole-green-fruit-selective-focus.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=UfuQNFGmYa2u8ibmimk8PemN-nR22pn389ZhCEmbZBc=" alt="Food 4">
