            <p>Zesty Sprite lemonade</p>
            <span class="arrow">&#9660;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
           <p>In a jug, pour chilled Sprite. Squeeze fresh lime juice into the jug.</p>
           <p> Stir in sugar to taste, as per your preference. Serve over ice and garnish with a slice of lime.</p>
           <p> Take a sip and enjoy it on a hot summer afternoon.</p>
